Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.Для\ каждого\ КлючИЗначение\ Из\ СтруктураКатегорий\ Цикл\nТекстЗапросаОбъект\ \=\ TekstZaprosaObekt\ +\ "\n|\tLEVOE\ Connection\ RegistrSvedeniy\.KategoriiObektov\ As\ Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key+"\n|\t\tPO\ "\ +\ PsevdonimTablitsy\ +\ "\.Ref\ \=\ Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key+"\.Object\n|\t\tI\ (Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key+"\.Kategoriya\ \=\ &"+KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key+")";\nKonetsTsikla;.Description=To kazhdogo KlyuchIZnachenie From StrukturaKategoriy Tsikl\nTekstZaprosaObekt \= TekstZaprosaObekt + "\n|\tLEVOE Connection RegistrSvedeniy.KategoriiObektov As Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie.Key+"\n|\t\tPO " + PsevdonimTablitsy + ".Ref \= Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie.Key+".Object\n|\t\tI (Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie.Key+".Kategoriya \= &"+KlyuchIZnachenie.Key+")";\nKonetsTsikla;
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.Для\ каждого\ КлючИЗначение\ Из\ СтруктураКатегорий\ Цикл\nТекстЗапросаОбъект\ \=\ TekstZaprosaObekt\ +\ ","\ +\ X\.PS\ +\n"\tVYBOR\ KOGDA\ Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key+"\.Kategoriya\ Has\ Null\ TOGDA\ LOZh\ INAChE\ ISTINA\ End\ As\ "\ +\ KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key;\nKonetsTsikla;.Description=To kazhdogo KlyuchIZnachenie From StrukturaKategoriy Tsikl\nTekstZaprosaObekt \= TekstZaprosaObekt + "," + X.PS +\n"\tVYBOR KOGDA Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie.Key+".Kategoriya Has Null TOGDA LOZh INAChE ISTINA End As " + KlyuchIZnachenie.Key;\nKonetsTsikla;
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.Для\ каждого\ КлючИЗначение\ Из\ СтруктураСвойств\ Цикл\nТекстЗапросаОбъект\ \=\ TekstZaprosaObekt\ +\ "\n|\tLEVOE\ Connection\ RegistrSvedeniy\.ZnacheniyaSvoystvObektov\ As\ Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key+"\n|\t\tPO\ "\ +\ PsevdonimTablitsy\ +\ "\.Ref\ \=\ Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key+"\.Object\n|\t\tI\ (Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key+"\.Property\ \=\ &"+KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key+")";\nKonetsTsikla;.Description=To kazhdogo KlyuchIZnachenie From StrukturaSvoystv Tsikl\nTekstZaprosaObekt \= TekstZaprosaObekt + "\n|\tLEVOE Connection RegistrSvedeniy.ZnacheniyaSvoystvObektov As Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie.Key+"\n|\t\tPO " + PsevdonimTablitsy + ".Ref \= Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie.Key+".Object\n|\t\tI (Tablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie.Key+".Property \= &"+KlyuchIZnachenie.Key+")";\nKonetsTsikla;
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.Для\ каждого\ КлючИЗначение\ Из\ СтруктураСвойств\ Цикл\nТекстЗапросаОбъект\ \=\ TekstZaprosaObekt\ +\ ","\ +\ X\.PS\ +\ "\tTablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key+"\.Value\ As\ "+KlyuchIZnachenie\.Key;\nKonetsTsikla;.Description=To kazhdogo KlyuchIZnachenie From StrukturaSvoystv Tsikl\nTekstZaprosaObekt \= TekstZaprosaObekt + "," + X.PS + "\tTablitsa_"+KlyuchIZnachenie.Key+".Value As "+KlyuchIZnachenie.Key;\nKonetsTsikla;
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.Если\ ВсегоСтрок\ \=\ 0\ Togda\nEsli\ Dont\ PostroitelZaprosa\ \=\ Neopredeleno\ T\ Dont\ PostroitelZaprosa\.Filter\ \=\ Neopredeleno\ Togda\nKolichestvoOtborov\ \=\ PostroitelZaprosa\.Filter\.Processed();\nDlya\ ZIP\ \=\ 1\ By\ KolichestvoOtborov\ Tsikl\nPostroitelZaprosa\.Filter\.Delete(KolichestvoOtborov\ -\ ZIP);\nKonetsTsikla;\nKonetsEsli;\nPostroitelZaprosa\ \=\ Neopredeleno;\nVozvrat;\nKonetsEsli;\nEsli\ PostroitelZaprosa\ \=\ Neopredeleno\ Togda\nPostroitelZaprosa\ \=\ New\ PostroitelZaprosa;\nKonetsEsli;.Description=If VsegoStrok \= 0 Togda\nEsli Dont PostroitelZaprosa \= Neopredeleno T Dont PostroitelZaprosa.Filter \= Neopredeleno Togda\nKolichestvoOtborov \= PostroitelZaprosa.Filter.Processed();\nDlya ZIP \= 1 By KolichestvoOtborov Tsikl\nPostroitelZaprosa.Filter.Delete(KolichestvoOtborov - ZIP);\nKonetsTsikla;\nKonetsEsli;\nPostroitelZaprosa \= Neopredeleno;\nVozvrat;\nKonetsEsli;\nEsli PostroitelZaprosa \= Neopredeleno Togda\nPostroitelZaprosa \= New PostroitelZaprosa;\nKonetsEsli;
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.Если\ ДоступностьВВебПриложенииНоменклатуры\ Тогда\nСписокПредставлений\.Добавить(Префикс+"Доступна\ в\ веб-приложении\ ""Управление\ заказами""","П_ДоступнаВВебПриложенииУпрЗаказами");\nКонецЕсли;.Description=If DostupnostVVebPrilozheniiNomenklatury Togda\nSpisokPredstavleniy.Add(Prefix+"Group In Web-Application ""Totals zakazami""","P_DostupnaVVebPrilozheniiUprZakazami");\nKonetsEsli;
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.Если\ КонтрольОстатковНоменклатуры\ Тогда\nСписокПредставлений\.Добавить(Префикс+"Остаток\ товара","Р_Остаток");\nСписокПредставлений\.Добавить(Префикс+"Остаток-Резерв\ товара","Р_Резерв");\nКонецЕсли;.Description=If KontrolOstatkovNomenklatury Togda\nSpisokPredstavleniy.Add(Prefix+"Balance tovara","R_Ostatok");\nSpisokPredstavleniy.Add(Prefix+"Balance-Rezerv tovara","R_Rezerv");\nKonetsEsli;
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.Если\ Объект\.ТипОбъекта\ \=\ 1\ Togda\nTekstZaprosaOkonchanie\ \=\ TekstZaprosaOkonchanie\ +\ "\n|Organize\ By\n|\tSh_Data,\n|\tObekt";\nPolyaSortirovki\ \=\ "Sh_Data,Object";\nInache\nTekstZaprosaOkonchanie\ \=\ TekstZaprosaOkonchanie\ +\ "\n|Organize\ By\n|\tSh_Vid,\n|\tObekt";\nPolyaSortirovki\ \=\ "Sh_Vid,Object";\nKonetsEsli;\nEsli\ Object\.ProcessTabularParts\ Togda\nTekstZaprosaOkonchanie\ \=\ TekstZaprosaOkonchanie\ +\ ",\n|\tT_TCh,\n|\tT_NomerStroki";\nPolyaSortirovki\ \=\ PolyaSortirovki\ +\ ",T_TCh,T_NomerStroki";\nKonetsEsli;.Description=If Object.ObjectType \= 1 Togda\nTekstZaprosaOkonchanie \= TekstZaprosaOkonchanie + "\n|Organize By\n|\tSh_Data,\n|\tObekt";\nPolyaSortirovki \= "Sh_Data,Object";\nInache\nTekstZaprosaOkonchanie \= TekstZaprosaOkonchanie + "\n|Organize By\n|\tSh_Vid,\n|\tObekt";\nPolyaSortirovki \= "Sh_Vid,Object";\nKonetsEsli;\nEsli Object.ProcessTabularParts Togda\nTekstZaprosaOkonchanie \= TekstZaprosaOkonchanie + ",\n|\tT_TCh,\n|\tT_NomerStroki";\nPolyaSortirovki \= PolyaSortirovki + ",T_TCh,T_NomerStroki";\nKonetsEsli;
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.Макет\ \=\ PoluchitMaket("PredopredelennyeRekvizity");\nOblast\ \=\ Template\.Title[?(Object\.ObjectType\ \=\ 0,"Spravochniki","Documents")];\nSchetchik\ \=\ 0;\nVidObekta\ \=\ "*";\nDlya\ S\ \=\ \ Duplicates\.Verkh\ By\ Duplicates\.Niz\ Tsikl\nTekVidObekta\ \=\ SokrLP(Template\.Duplicates("R"+S+"C1")\.Text);\nEsli\ \ TekVidObekta\ <>\ ""\ Togda\nEsli\ TekVidObekta\ \=\ "*"\ Togda\nVidObekta\ \=\ TekVidObekta;\nInache\nVidObekta\ \=\ TekVidObekta;\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsEsli;\nEsli\ ImyaVidaOdnogoTipa\ \=\ VidObekta\ Or\ VidObekta\ \=\ "*"\ Togda\nPolnoeImyaRekvizita\ \=\ SokrLP(Template\.Duplicates("R"+S+"C2")\.Text);\nOpisanie\ \=\ SokrLP(Template\.Duplicates("R"+S+"C3")\.Text);\nCherezTochku\ \=\ Lozh;\nPozTChK\ \=\ Find(PolnoeImyaRekvizita,"\.");\nEtoSostavnoyRekvizit\ \=\ Dont(PozTChK\ \=\ 0);\nImyaKornya\ \=\ "Sh_"+?(PozTChK\ \=\ 0,PolnoeImyaRekvizita,Lev(PolnoeImyaRekvizita,PozTChK-1));\nPoleNastroyki\ \=\ PostroitelZaprosa\.DostupnyePolya\.Find(ImyaKornya);\nPoka\ Dont\ PozTChK\ \=\ 0\ T\ Dont\ PoleNastroyki\ \=\ Neopredeleno\ Tsikl\n\tPolnoeImyaRekvizita\ \=\ Sred(PolnoeImyaRekvizita,PozTChK+1);\n\tPozTChK\ \=\ Find(PolnoeImyaRekvizita,"\.");\n\tPoleNastroyki\ \=\ PoleNastroyki\.Fields\.Find(?(PozTChK\ \=\ 0,PolnoeImyaRekvizita,Lev(PolnoeImyaRekvizita,PozTChK-1)));\n\tCherezTochku\ \=\ Istina;\nKonetsTsikla;\nEsli\ Dont\ PoleNastroyki\ \=\ Neopredeleno\ Togda\nEsli\ EtoSostavnoyRekvizit\ Togda\nSchetchik\ \=\ Schetchik+1;\nPostroitelZaprosa\.VybrannyePolya\.Add(PoleNastroyki\.PutKDannym,"D_"+Schetchik);\nSpisokPredstavleniy\.Add(Description,"D_"+Schetchik);\nPredopredelennyeRekvizity\.Add(New\ Structure("Name,PoleNastroyki","D_"+Schetchik,PoleNastroyki),Description);\nInache\nPredopredelennyeRekvizity\.Add(New\ Structure("Name,PoleNastroyki",PoleNastroyki\.Name,PoleNastroyki),Description);\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsTsikla;\n\n\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\nPostroitelZaprosa_Otbor\ \=\ PostroitelZaprosa\.Filter;\nPostroitelZaprosa\.DobavleniePredstavleniy\ \=\ TipDobavleniyaPredstavleniy\.NeDobavlyat;.Description=Template \= PoluchitMaket("PredopredelennyeRekvizity");\nOblast \= Template.Title[?(Object.ObjectType \= 0,"Spravochniki","Documents")];\nSchetchik \= 0;\nVidObekta \= "*";\nDlya S \=  Duplicates.Verkh By Duplicates.Niz Tsikl\nTekVidObekta \= SokrLP(Template.Duplicates("R"+S+"C1").Text);\nEsli  TekVidObekta <> "" Togda\nEsli TekVidObekta \= "*" Togda\nVidObekta \= TekVidObekta;\nInache\nVidObekta \= TekVidObekta;\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsEsli;\nEsli ImyaVidaOdnogoTipa \= VidObekta Or VidObekta \= "*" Togda\nPolnoeImyaRekvizita \= SokrLP(Template.Duplicates("R"+S+"C2").Text);\nOpisanie \= SokrLP(Template.Duplicates("R"+S+"C3").Text);\nCherezTochku \= Lozh;\nPozTChK \= Find(PolnoeImyaRekvizita,".");\nEtoSostavnoyRekvizit \= Dont(PozTChK \= 0);\nImyaKornya \= "Sh_"+?(PozTChK \= 0,PolnoeImyaRekvizita,Lev(PolnoeImyaRekvizita,PozTChK-1));\nPoleNastroyki \= PostroitelZaprosa.DostupnyePolya.Find(ImyaKornya);\nPoka Dont PozTChK \= 0 T Dont PoleNastroyki \= Neopredeleno Tsikl\n\tPolnoeImyaRekvizita \= Sred(PolnoeImyaRekvizita,PozTChK+1);\n\tPozTChK \= Find(PolnoeImyaRekvizita,".");\n\tPoleNastroyki \= PoleNastroyki.Fields.Find(?(PozTChK \= 0,PolnoeImyaRekvizita,Lev(PolnoeImyaRekvizita,PozTChK-1)));\n\tCherezTochku \= Istina;\nKonetsTsikla;\nEsli Dont PoleNastroyki \= Neopredeleno Togda\nEsli EtoSostavnoyRekvizit Togda\nSchetchik \= Schetchik+1;\nPostroitelZaprosa.VybrannyePolya.Add(PoleNastroyki.PutKDannym,"D_"+Schetchik);\nSpisokPredstavleniy.Add(Description,"D_"+Schetchik);\nPredopredelennyeRekvizity.Add(New Structure("Name,PoleNastroyki","D_"+Schetchik,PoleNastroyki),Description);\nInache\nPredopredelennyeRekvizity.Add(New Structure("Name,PoleNastroyki",PoleNastroyki.Name,PoleNastroyki),Description);\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsTsikla;\n\n\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\nPostroitelZaprosa_Otbor \= PostroitelZaprosa.Filter;\nPostroitelZaprosa.DobavleniePredstavleniy \= TipDobavleniyaPredstavleniy.NeDobavlyat;
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.МассивНастроекОтбора\ \ \ \ \ \=\ New\ Array;.Description=MassivNastroekOtbora     \= New Array;
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.ОписаниеВсехТипов\ \=\ New\ OpisanieTipov(MassivTipov);.Description=OpisanieVsekhTipov \= New OpisanieTipov(MassivTipov);
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.ПостроительЗапроса\.Текст\ \=\ ArbitraryQueryText;\nPostroitelZaprosa\.FillSettings();\nKolichestvoPoley\ \=\ PostroitelZaprosa\.DostupnyePolya\.Processed();\nDlya\ S\ \=\ 0\ By\ KolichestvoPoley\ -\ 1\ Tsikl\nDostupnoePole\ \=\ PostroitelZaprosa\.DostupnyePolya[KolichestvoPoley\ -\ S\ -\ 1];\nEsli\ PostroitelZaprosa\.VybrannyePolya\.Find(DostupnoePole\.Name)\ \=\ Neopredeleno\ Togda\nPostroitelZaprosa\.DostupnyePolya\.Delete(DostupnoePole);\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsTsikla;\nKolichestvoPoley\ \=\ PostroitelZaprosa\.VybrannyePolya\.Processed();\nDlya\ S\ \=\ 0\ By\ KolichestvoPoley\ -\ 1\ Tsikl\nImyaPolya\ \=\ PostroitelZaprosa\.VybrannyePolya[KolichestvoPoley\ -\ S\ -\ 1]\.Name;\nDostupnoePole\ \=\ PostroitelZaprosa\.DostupnyePolya\.Find(ImyaPolya);\nPostroitelZaprosa\.DostupnyePolya\.Sdvinut(DostupnoePole,-1000);\nKonetsTsikla;\nDlya\ kazhdogo\ ElementPredstavleniya\ From\ SpisokPredstavleniy\ Tsikl\nDostupnoePole\ \=\ PostroitelZaprosa\.DostupnyePolya\.Find(ElementPredstavleniya\.Presentation);\nEsli\ Dont\ DostupnoePole\ \=\ Neopredeleno\ Togda\nDostupnoePole\.Presentation\ \=\ PoluchitPredstavlenie(ElementPredstavleniya);\nEsli\ Lev(DostupnoePole\.Name\ ,\ 2)\ \=\ "S_"\ Togda\nDostupnoePole\.TipZnacheniya\ \=\ StrukturaSvoystv[DostupnoePole\.Name]\.TipZnacheniya;\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsTsikla;\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora\ \=\ PostroitelZaprosa\.Filter\.PoluchitDostupnyePolya();\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora\.Delete(AvailableFilterFields\.Sh_VidPredstavlenie);\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora\.Sh_Ssylka\.Fields\.Clear();\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora\.Delete(AvailableFilterFields\.Sh_Ssylka);\nEsli\ Object\.ProcessTabularParts\ Togda\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora\.Delete(AvailableFilterFields\.T_TChPredstavlenie);\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora\.Delete(AvailableFilterFields\.T_TCh);\nKonetsEsli;\n\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\ VOSSTANOVLENIE\ Manager\ Rules\ PREDYDUShchEGO\ Text\nDlya\ kazhdogo\ ElementOtbora\ From\ MassivNastroekOtbora\ Tsikl\nDostupnoePole\ \=\ AvailableFilterFields\.Find(ElementOtbora\.PutKDannym);\nPopytka\nNovyyElementOtbora\ \=\ PostroitelZaprosa\.Filter\.Add(ElementOtbora\.PutKDannym);\nNovyyElementOtbora\.Use\ \=\ ElementOtbora\.Use;\nNovyyElementOtbora\.VidSravneniya\ \=\ ElementOtbora\.VidSravneniya;\nNovyyElementOtbora\.Value\ \=\ ElementOtbora\.Value;\nNovyyElementOtbora\.ZnachenieS\ \=\ ElementOtbora\.ZnachenieS;\nNovyyElementOtbora\.ZnacheniePo\ \=\ ElementOtbora\.ZnacheniePo;\nIsklyuchenie\nKonetsPopytki;\nKonetsTsikla;.Description=PostroitelZaprosa.Text \= ArbitraryQueryText;\nPostroitelZaprosa.FillSettings();\nKolichestvoPoley \= PostroitelZaprosa.DostupnyePolya.Processed();\nDlya S \= 0 By KolichestvoPoley - 1 Tsikl\nDostupnoePole \= PostroitelZaprosa.DostupnyePolya[KolichestvoPoley - S - 1];\nEsli PostroitelZaprosa.VybrannyePolya.Find(DostupnoePole.Name) \= Neopredeleno Togda\nPostroitelZaprosa.DostupnyePolya.Delete(DostupnoePole);\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsTsikla;\nKolichestvoPoley \= PostroitelZaprosa.VybrannyePolya.Processed();\nDlya S \= 0 By KolichestvoPoley - 1 Tsikl\nImyaPolya \= PostroitelZaprosa.VybrannyePolya[KolichestvoPoley - S - 1].Name;\nDostupnoePole \= PostroitelZaprosa.DostupnyePolya.Find(ImyaPolya);\nPostroitelZaprosa.DostupnyePolya.Sdvinut(DostupnoePole,-1000);\nKonetsTsikla;\nDlya kazhdogo ElementPredstavleniya From SpisokPredstavleniy Tsikl\nDostupnoePole \= PostroitelZaprosa.DostupnyePolya.Find(ElementPredstavleniya.Presentation);\nEsli Dont DostupnoePole \= Neopredeleno Togda\nDostupnoePole.Presentation \= PoluchitPredstavlenie(ElementPredstavleniya);\nEsli Lev(DostupnoePole.Name , 2) \= "S_" Togda\nDostupnoePole.TipZnacheniya \= StrukturaSvoystv[DostupnoePole.Name].TipZnacheniya;\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsEsli;\nKonetsTsikla;\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora \= PostroitelZaprosa.Filter.PoluchitDostupnyePolya();\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora.Delete(AvailableFilterFields.Sh_VidPredstavlenie);\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora.Sh_Ssylka.Fields.Clear();\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora.Delete(AvailableFilterFields.Sh_Ssylka);\nEsli Object.ProcessTabularParts Togda\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora.Delete(AvailableFilterFields.T_TChPredstavlenie);\nDostupnyePolyaOtbora.Delete(AvailableFilterFields.T_TCh);\nKonetsEsli;\n\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\=\= VOSSTANOVLENIE Manager Rules PREDYDUShchEGO Text\nDlya kazhdogo ElementOtbora From MassivNastroekOtbora Tsikl\nDostupnoePole \= AvailableFilterFields.Find(ElementOtbora.PutKDannym);\nPopytka\nNovyyElementOtbora \= PostroitelZaprosa.Filter.Add(ElementOtbora.PutKDannym);\nNovyyElementOtbora.Use \= ElementOtbora.Use;\nNovyyElementOtbora.VidSravneniya \= ElementOtbora.VidSravneniya;\nNovyyElementOtbora.Value \= ElementOtbora.Value;\nNovyyElementOtbora.ZnachenieS \= ElementOtbora.ZnachenieS;\nNovyyElementOtbora.ZnacheniePo \= ElementOtbora.ZnacheniePo;\nIsklyuchenie\nKonetsPopytki;\nKonetsTsikla;
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.ТекстЗапроса\ \=\ GetQueryText();.Description=ArbitraryQueryText \= GetQueryText();
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.ТекстЗапросаОбъект\ \=\ TekstZaprosaObekt\ +\ ","\ +\ "\n|\tVYBOR\n|\t\tKOGDA\ Tablitsa_P_Veb\.Product\ Has\ Null\ TOGDA\ Istina\n|\t\tINAChE\ Lozh\n|\tKONETs\ As\ P_DostupnaVVebPrilozheniiUprZakazami";.Description=TekstZaprosaObekt \= TekstZaprosaObekt + "," + "\n|\tVYBOR\n|\t\tKOGDA Tablitsa_P_Veb.Product Has Null TOGDA Istina\n|\t\tINAChE Lozh\n|\tKONETs As P_DostupnaVVebPrilozheniiUprZakazami";
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.ТекстЗапросаОбъект\ \=\ TekstZaprosaObekt\ +\ ","\ +\ "\n|\tESTNULL(Tablitsa_R_Ostatok\.KolichestvoOstatok,0)\ As\ R_Ostatok,\n|\tESTNULL(Tablitsa_R_Ostatok\.KolichestvoOstatok,\ 0)\ -\ ESTNULL(Tablitsa_R_Rezerv\.KolichestvoOstatok,\ 0)\ As\ R_Rezerv";.Description=TekstZaprosaObekt \= TekstZaprosaObekt + "," + "\n|\tESTNULL(Tablitsa_R_Ostatok.KolichestvoOstatok,0) As R_Ostatok,\n|\tESTNULL(Tablitsa_R_Ostatok.KolichestvoOstatok, 0) - ESTNULL(Tablitsa_R_Rezerv.KolichestvoOstatok, 0) As R_Rezerv";
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.ТекстЗапросаОбъект\ \=\ TekstZaprosaObekt\ +\ ","\ +\ "\n|\tLEVOE\ Connection\ RegistrNakopleniya\.TovaryNaSkladakh\.Balance\ As\ Tablitsa_R_Ostatok\n|\t\tPO\ "\ +\ PsevdonimTablitsy\ +\ "\.Ref\ \=\ Tablitsa_R_Ostatok\.Product\n|\tLEVOE\ Connection\ RegistrNakopleniya\.TovaryVRezerveNaSkladakh\.Balance\ As\ Tablitsa_R_Rezerv\n|\t\tPO\ "\ +\ PsevdonimTablitsy\ +\ "\.Ref\ \=\ Tablitsa_R_Rezerv\.Product";.Description=TekstZaprosaObekt \= TekstZaprosaObekt + "," + "\n|\tLEVOE Connection RegistrNakopleniya.TovaryNaSkladakh.Balance As Tablitsa_R_Ostatok\n|\t\tPO " + PsevdonimTablitsy + ".Ref \= Tablitsa_R_Ostatok.Product\n|\tLEVOE Connection RegistrNakopleniya.TovaryVRezerveNaSkladakh.Balance As Tablitsa_R_Rezerv\n|\t\tPO " + PsevdonimTablitsy + ".Ref \= Tablitsa_R_Rezerv.Product";
Method.ИнициализацияЗапроса.Comment.ТекстЗапросаОбъект\ \=\ TekstZaprosaObekt\ +\ ","\ +\ "\n|\tLEVOE\ Connection\ RegistrSvedeniy\.NomenklaturaNeispolzuemayaVVebUpravleniiZakazami\ As\ Tablitsa_P_Veb\n|\tPO\ "\ +\ PsevdonimTablitsy\ +\ "\.Ref\ \=\ Tablitsa_P_Veb\.Product";.Description=TekstZaprosaObekt \= TekstZaprosaObekt + "," + "\n|\tLEVOE Connection RegistrSvedeniy.NomenklaturaNeispolzuemayaVVebUpravleniiZakazami As Tablitsa_P_Veb\n|\tPO " + PsevdonimTablitsy + ".Ref \= Tablitsa_P_Veb.Product";
